reviewText: Was overpriced for 1 disc, so I returned it.  Was not worth the money, but I did get a full refund.  Customer service was excellent.

Nicely done, but I believe more time could have been devoted to the gorgeous squares in Savannah, one of the most beautiful cities in the U. S.  I recommend this to someone who has never visited the city.
Iam sorry to give just one star, because I never received the video and did not know where to complain, I don't even remember whether I was charged.
